{"tid":1672115,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[問題, 求指教] 離岸銀行戶口 vs 離岸證券戶口","createTime":"2019-10-24T02:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T05:20:42.000Z","uid":219470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c22c5c1b43c4de8f37c5a73217784a322f99dfd9","tid":1672115,"uid":219470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T02:14:19.000Z","msg":"本身有個離岸證券戶口, 亦都存左一大筆錢落去買美股<br />\n呢排順手研究埋離岸銀行戶口 (包括 Citi, HSBC, Barclays), 但發現其實以上銀行戶口有 minimum balance requirement 之餘 (金額仲唔細), 亦都未必有好似證券戶口咁嘅投資服務, 就算有, 投資買股嘅手續費亦都比證券戶口貴好多<br />\n照咁睇, 其實係咪無太大必要另外開過個離岸銀行戶口?<br />\n唔該曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0dff068cf5a00bb25d99ab916311799039698df","tid":1672115,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T02:16:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【SUCK／1026】長龍爆買日 - 黃店存貨壓力測試（2）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1672101\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1672101</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/guewjRY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FguewjRY.jpg&h=ac95176a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2d1773c2385d35dea4f1c25389278917ed6d1591","tid":1672115,"uid":219470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T02:29:03.000Z","msg":"push <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1531a4cab24129b87663f99a9225fe4397afe2ae","tid":1672115,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T02:44:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1yYtmny.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1yYtmny.gif&h=db5af89f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51da4ccdb5780119c9ee246bb367eb1d2de71147","tid":1672115,"uid":219470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T02:52:20.000Z","msg":"push <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a98f7ccb5eb6e430158d832542322aebf90ca67","tid":16